### student courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/courses/enrolled
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Example response (do not paste live responses here uncommented — REST Client parses the whole file as requests):
# HTTP/1.1 200
# ETag: "8pOJJfXydAdd7hO9XJpMix2NunDvVlG5g2RUPr+ZU0umD5w2l1A6VbZFbxWpkP+lRwmJsUUN0KGyr2O2sXFZ6g=="
# Content-Type: application/json
# ...
# { "items": [ ... ], "hasMore": false, ... }

### course detail
